ſtrengthen my ſelfe, and vvronge not them. 3. Doctour Prideaux vpon the Sabbath, lately comne forth, pag. 140. ſaith. Where did Chriſt abrogate the Sabbath? vvhere is there any mention of ſetting the Lords day in the roome of it? well, Chriſt aſcendeth, he left his Apoſtles preachers, and did not they vvithout any ſcruple obſerue the Sabbath of the Iewes, wich the Iewes? did not they inſtitute moſt freely aſſemblies in the Sabbath day? & did not the ſucceding churches the like, &c?
